VALUES ('77c581ae-2760-4c18-acc4-e5514eb42693', 'Which choice best uses data from the table to evaluate the researchers'' hypothesis?', 'Researchers compared soil-carbon storage under two methods across two depths after twenty years. They hypothesize that Method A increases storage relative to Method B at shallow depth, but that at deep depth the relationship inverts.

The table summarizes the results.

| Method | Shallow (20 yr) | Deep (20 yr) |
| --- | --- | --- |
| A | $22\text{ g/kg}$ | $29\text{ g/kg}$ |
